      "beast_baseline": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start, the flow is definitely there. The script gave it a decent score, but it's a bit on the lower side for what I'm looking for. I want the \"fact density\" to be much more robust so students can see all the key players and dates clearly.\n\nCan you try another version? Try to incorporate more specific names, places, and dates from the era to bump up that score, but again—please make sure it still reads like a proper, cohesive textbook summary. I don't want a list; I want a rich, detailed narrative.",
